<!--
VOICING PLAN:
- Key D, 6/4. Three half-note chord beats per bar. LH "33" root position dominant.
- Chromatic non-diatonic chords (G#°7, G#, F#+) substituted with diatonic equivalents (Em, A7, F#m).
- Climax bar 7-8 uses G# augmented approach as Em7, resolves to A7-D.

VOICE LEADING HIGHLIGHTS:
- LH bass line D→E→A→D stepwise in bars 1-2; contrary motion against descending melody.
- RH climbs to E5 at bar 10 (highest point), then descends stepwise to close.

TEXTURE ARC:
- Full six-beat bars build steadily to climax (bar 9-11); final resolution spreads quietly to bar 16.
-->
